    <summary>HTTP to Gemini proxy</summary>
    <categories>
        <category>Network</category>
    </categories>
    <keywords>
        <keyword>Gemini</keyword>
        <keyword>Proxy</keyword>
    </keywords>

    <description>
        <p>
            levior is a web-to-Gemini proxy written in Python3 with asyncio
            and aiogemini. It converts web pages on-the-fly to the gemtext format,
            allowing you to browse regular web pages with
            any Gemini browser without having to suffer the heavyness associated
            with certain technologies of the modern web.
        </p>
    </description>

